OL,5, A son claims his mother's body was     
OL,6, found "decomposing" in a Hull funeral  
OL,7, parlour months after he was told she   
OL,8, had been cremated.                     
OL,10,FJessie Stockdale, described as a       
OL,11,Fgrandmother who "everyone loved", died 
OL,12,Fin November last year.                 
OL,14,FHer family used Legacy Independent     
OL,15,FFuneral Directors, now at the centre of
OL,16,Fa major police investigation.          
OL,18,FColin Stockdale alleges police told his
OL,19,Ffamily they suspect she is one of 35   
OL,20,Fbodies recovered from the parlour.     
